msgid ""
"<strong>You didn't import demo data?</strong> You can still do it. Go to "
"Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Hardware Shop package and check the "
"related box."
msgstr ""
"<strong>¿No importó los datos de demostración?</strong> Todavía puede "
"hacerlo. Vaya a Aplicaciones &gt; Sectores, actualice el paquete para "
"ferreterías y seleccione la casilla correspondiente."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Website</span></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders directly "
"in Odoo and go live with your <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">E-"
"shop</span></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"Un <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">sitio web</span></strong> "
"gratuito, personalizado e integrado en unos pocos clics. Comience a recibir "
"pedidos directamente en Odoo o habilite su <strong><span style=\"color: "
"#875A7B;\">tienda en línea</span></strong> en tan solo unos minutos."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
