#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Let's say your customer Ace Hardware just called you to order 30 Asian. "
"Water Proofing Hydroloc."
msgstr ""
"Supongamos que su cliente Ace Hardware acaba de pedir 30 unidades de "
"impermeabilizante Asian"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><span "
"style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Marketing Automation</span></strong>, "
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Email Marketing</span></strong>, "
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Social Media Marketing</span></"
"strong>, and <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">SMS Marketing</span></"
"strong>"
msgstr ""
"Gestione todos sus canales de comunicación en un solo lugar con las "
"aplicaciones <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Automatización de "
"marketing</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Marketing "
"por correo electrónico</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Marketing social</span></strong> y <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Marketing por SMS</span></strong> de Odoo."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Accounting App</span></"
"strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Gestione su contabilidad con mayor facilidad gracias a un entorno "
"completamente integrado. (<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Contabilidad</span></strong>)"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.template,name:hardware_shop.product_template_70
msgid "Mario Super Water Tank"
msgstr "Reservorio de agua Mario Super"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Navigate to the Inventory App and select \"X to process\" in the Delivery "
"Orders."
msgstr ""
"Vaya a Inventario y seleccione “X a procesar” en las órdenes de entrega."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Navigate to your Sales App. You can now create a new Sales Order by clicking "
"the \"New\" button, top left."
msgstr ""
"Vaya a Ventas. Ahora puede crear un nuevo pedido de venta si hace clic en el "
"botón “Nuevo” que se encuentra en la parte superior izquierda."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Notice that if you need the delivery to be paid by your customer, you can "
"create a delivery product and add it to its cart. In this demo, you can use "
"the \"POS Delivery\" to add a 5,00 Excl. Taxes delivery price."
msgstr ""
"Considere que si necesita que el cliente pague la entrega, entonces puede "
"crear un producto de entrega y añadirlo a su cesta. En esta demostración "
"puede utilizar “Entrega del TPV” para añadir un precio de entrega de 5,00 € "
"(no incluye impuestos)."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that we have placed all these orders, it's time to purchase missing "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Luego de realizar todas estos pedidos, es momento de comprar los productos "
"faltantes."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into "
"an additional scanner (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo está totalmente integrado en una aplicación. Descárguela para convertir "
"su móvil en un escáner adicional (y mucho más)."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo le ofrece posibilidades infinitas, como:"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Este solo es un resumen de las funciones incluidas en este paquete. Añada "
"nuevas aplicaciones, elimine o modifique los datos de demostración y pruebe "
"todas las funciones."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the order is placed, you can see that the top left button switches to "
"\"Receive products\". Click it to open your receipt order and validate it to "
"confirm that this product is back in stock."
msgstr ""
"Luego de realizar el pedido verá que el botón situado del lado superior "
"izquierdo cambia a “Recibir productos”. Haga clic para abrir su orden de "
"recepción y valídela para confirmar que este producto está disponible otra "
"vez."

